   <div class="teaser_fmt"> 
    <h3>Metabolic Syndrome</h3> 
    <p>Metabolic syndrome is a group of risk factors -- high blood pressure, high blood sugar, high triglycerides, low HDL cholesterol, and belly fat -- that increases risk of heart disease and diabetes. Diet, exercise, and medications can help improve it. </p> 
